figure_1.title: Figure 1. Map of Relative Uptake of Medicare Obesity Benefit, by state, 2013.
figure_1.caption: The proportion of number of beneficiaries using the Medicare Obesity Benefit and the number of estimated beneficiaries with obesity eligible for the benefit by state in the United States in the year 2013. Data was suppressed in 10 states.
